Any such formula_64 is commonly called a section of &quot;formula_84&quot;, and this example is the reason why the elements in formula_8 are generally called sections. This construction is especially important when formula_84 is the projection of a fiber bundle onto its base space. For example, the sheaves of smooth functions are the sheaves of sections of the trivial bundle. 

Another example: the sheaf of sections of
