(this is also called a sheaf extension.)

Let formula_254 be sheaves of abelian groups. The set formula_255 of morphisms of sheaves from formula_72 to formula_257 forms an abelian group (by the abelian group structure of formula_257). The sheaf hom of formula_72 and formula_257, denoted by,
