where formula_529 is the derived functor. This latter functor encompasses the notion of sheaf cohomology since formula_530 for formula_531.
Like formula_526, the direct image with compact support formula_533 can also be derived. By virtue of the following isomorphism formula_534 parametrizes the cohomology with compact support of the fibers of formula_84:
:formula_536
This isomorphism is an example of a base change theorem. There is another adjunction
