<doc id="245551" wikidata="Q803755" url="?curid=245551" title="Baiji (disambiguation)">
<text>[[Baiji]] is a species of dolphin, the Yangtze River dolphin (&quot;Lipotes vexillifer&quot;).

Baiji may also refer to:

* Baiji, Iraq, a city
* Baiji District, Iraq
* Baiji Township, Xiuning County (), Anhui, China
* Baiji Township, Nanning (), in Yongning District, Nanning, Guangxi, China
* An ancient kingdom in the southern Korean peninsula, called Baekje in Korean

==See also==
* Bahjí
* Baijiu</text><links>
